{"tid":812084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"26年來首起日本豬瘟 岐阜縣養殖場撲殺610頭豬","createTime":"2018-09-09T11:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T15:37:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0291e368534097f169c7ada9f884f8f057aecd","tid":812084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"26年來首起日本豬瘟 岐阜縣養殖場撲殺610頭豬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2545878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2545878&d=UYZM1tQsFbWjGLhbwLF%2BfghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=17d77d0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2545878&h=8dac20e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2545878</a><br />\n<br />\n2018-09-09 14:04<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國上月爆發非洲豬瘟等疫情，日本農業部門今（9）日發布消息，指稱岐阜縣政府近日接獲報告，該地區一間養殖戶有80頭豬隻不明死亡，成為當地26以來首起豬瘟案例。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，日本農業部門指出，岐阜縣一間養豬場在上週之內，有80頭豬隻不明死亡。調查人員追蹤疾病來源後，表示死亡豬隻疑似受到外來豬隻感染，不過感染源與非洲豬瘟不同，這種病毒也不會傳染給人類。<br />\n<br />\n日本家畜傳染病預防條例規定，若有養殖場內豬隻被感染，就需撲殺場內所有豬隻。岐阜縣政府也表示，今天一早出動2500作業人員，預計要將該養殖場610頭豬隻全都撲殺。<br />\n<br />\n為避免瘟情擴大，該間養殖場半徑10公里範圍內皆被認為是危險範圍，同區域另外3間養殖場也被禁止出貨。這起瘟情為日本自1992年在熊本縣發生豬瘟疫情以來，時隔26年再度發生的案例。<br />\n<br />\n唔好呀~~~唔好燒到日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918e941267fd1329bbc2f52b97365b46537a2b5b","tid":812084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba7821e6dee8c111e5ea76d3e40622e772d3fc9","tid":812084,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8a958d4037e6bfede9386a513d711ad00e3f49","tid":812084,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f3c78a39e1eeed2b022200f528121caee376b8","tid":812084,"uid":145428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"世界末日要來臨吧"},{"pid":"7af1640e66fb57f91d9cd3c83c6bb7d36b798811","tid":812084,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:26:40.000Z","msg":"香港應停止輸入日本食品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01fd91d23fb3a1daf5b627e8a6de0f6ef410294","tid":812084,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"中國送禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f57b5a447941ab8bd2e13d859ed62042fd4a54","tid":812084,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}